void atmi::Queue::setQoS ( long  qos)

Set the desired persistence mode (memory, disk, default) Accepted values are : TPQQOSDEFAULTPERSIST: uses the persistence mode defined with queue TPQQOSPERSISTENT: message are written onto persistent storage TPQQOSNONPERSISTENT: message are written into memory only (message are lost if the queue manager is interrupted)

Parameters:
qosdesired flags
